
# RichnessEstimator
Code and data for:
An improved species richness estimator using spatial abundance data
Eden W. Tekwa(1,2,3*), Matthew A. Whalen(2,4,5), Patrick T. Martone(4), Mary I. Oâ€™Connor(1)

